The code chunk adds specific uniform parameters to shader code based on the presence of certain rendering settings ("VolumetricLighting" and "ExposureAdjust") in the configuration, which is part of a larger system for managing graphics effects and rendering quality.

if "VolumetricLighting" in configuration:
                text += "  uniform float4 k_casterpos,\n"
                text += "  uniform float4 k_vlparams,\n"

            if "ExposureAdjust" in configuration:
                text += "  uniform float k_exposure,\n"
